        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/marrakesh/_scene_spider.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 1ccadf6e-95b9-4f65-9026-abaa91aaccb4).Image",
        "Description": "Hello Agent,\rThis contract is urgent. Our client had a mole in Zaydan&apos;s ranks, but his cover was blown, and he is now facing a &quot;special&quot; interrogation. You must intercept Reyza&apos;s plans and prevent any information from being revealed. Your targets are the people with whom the mole spent the most time with. Since the mole&apos;s loyalty is now in question, he is also part of your contract. His death must appear accidental so as to avoid raising suspicion.\r\rGood luck.\r\rBy Lord_RedHelmet",
